text: Dera Ismail Khan is a city in Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan Dera Ismail Khan may also refer to: *Dera Ismail Khan District, a district of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan *Dera Ismail Khan Tehsil, a tehsil of Dera Ismail Khan District *Dera Ismail Khan Division, an administrative unit of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa, Pakistan *Dera Ismail Khan Cantonment, a cantonment in Pakistan *Dera Ismail Khan Airport *Dera Ismail Khan cricket team, a local and domestic cricket team ==See also== *Dera Ismail Khan mine, a large gypsum mine * * * Dera Ghazi Khan
